data.description: UNIQUE HESPERIA HOME WITH SOLAR, AND A LARGE WORKSHOP, PERFECT FOR THE BUSINESS OF YOUR DREAMS!! 750 square foot METAL WORKSHOP with a 10' x 10' roll up door, skylights, windows. Workshop has water and power. GREAT ORGANIC MINI-FARM on 1.3 acres of Land! There is a Livestock pen, chicken coop, WALIPINI greenhouse for year-round growing, fruit and nut trees. It even has Hydro-panels to make water from the air!! RV site has full hook ups, WIFI, Shed and connected yard for little dogs. Property is Fully fenced with cross fencing and double gates. The front porch welcomes you as you enter. The freestanding wood burning stove has a handmade custom mantel and is perfect for cold winter nights. Spacious Living Room and dining rooms are Bright and look out at the lovely trees, plants and sitting areas in the front yard. Work benches in the 2 car attached garage, Indoor laundry and a MUD/STORAGE Room that leads you to the back yard. Beautiful knotty-pine cabinetry in kitchen and hallways. Three Bedrooms PLUS BONUS ROOM with a large closet. The Bonus Room has its own Front Door and Porch with Parking space. Great for Multi Functions or for extra Family or extra income! The Main Bedroom also features a wood burning brick fireplace and lots of closet space. The galley kitchen has a breakfast nook area. This home has dual-pane windows and many places to park with security lights and flood lights. The Refrigerator, Washer and Dryer are included. 2 SEMI TRUCKS may be permitted to park on the property with City of Hesperia approval. VERY LOW UTILITY BILLS and Easy access to the freeway and shopping and close to Restaurant Row. Bring your horses and your RV. THE POSSIBILITIES ARE ENDLESS with this Home!!! Buyer to verify all information.
